; flex-direction: column; --ds-virtual-list-width: 492px;"><div class="ds-virtual-list-items _6f2c522" style="box-sizing: content-box; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 24px; padding-left: calc((100% - var(--message-list-max-width)) / 2); padding-right: calc((100% - var(--message-list-max-width)) / 2); flex-shrink: 0; flex-grow: 1; min-height: 70112px;"><div class="ds-virtual-list-visible-items" style="position: relative; transform: translateY(67949px); --ds-virtual-list-transform-y: 67949px; --ds-virtual-list-ios-compensation-y: 0px;"><div class="_4f9bf79 _43c05b5" data-virtual-list-item-key="299" style="--assistant-last-margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="ds-message _63c77b1" style="--panel-width: 0px;"><div class="ds-markdown" style="--ds-md-zoom: 1.143;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Понял, SVG не отображается правильно в конвертере. Сделаем проще — </span><strong><span>готовый PNG через онлайн-генератор иконок</span></strong><span>:</span></p><ol start="1"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Открой: </span><a href="https://www.favicon-generator.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><span>https://www.favicon-generator.org</span></a></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Прокрути до </span><strong><span>"Create your own favicon"</span></strong></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Нажми </span><strong><span>"Try it now"</span></strong></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Выбери любой цвет фона (например фиолетовый </span><code>#6C5CE7</code><span>)</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Нарисуй кексик 🧁 или напиши </span><strong><span>CC</span></strong></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Нажми </span><strong><span>"Create Favicon"</span></strong></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Скачай ZIP</span></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Достань оттуда </span><code>android-icon-192x192.png</code><span> и </span><code>apple-icon-180x180.png</code></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Переименуй их в </span><code>icon-192.png</code><span> и </span><code>icon-512.png</code></p></li><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span>Положи в папку </span><code>C:\Users\papa\confectioner-calc\deploy\</code></p></li></ol><hr><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><strong><span>Или ещё быстрее</span></strong><span> — давай я создам минималистичную иконку текстом:</span></p><div class="md-code-block md-code-block-dark"><div class="md-code-block-banner-wrap"><div class="md-code-block-banner md-code-block-banner-lite"><div class="_121d384"><div class="d2a24f03"><span class="d813de27">powershell</span></div><div class="d2a24f03 _246a029"><div class="efa13877"><button role="button" aria-disabled="false" class="ds-atom-button ds-text-button ds-text-button--with-icon" style="margin-right: 4px;"><div class="ds-icon ds-atom-button__icon" style="font-size: 16px; width: 16px; height: 16px; margin-right: 3px;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.14929 4.02032C7.11197 4.02032 7.87983 4.02016 8.49597 4.07598C9.12128 4.13269 9.65792 4.25188 10.1415 4.53106C10.7202 4.8653 11.2008 5.3459 11.535 5.92462C11.8142 6.40818 11.9334 6.94481 11.9901 7.57012C12.0459 8.18625 12.0458 8.95419 12.0458 9.9168C12.0458 10.8795 12.0459 11.6473 11.9901 12.2635C11.9334 12.8888 11.8142 13.4254 11.535 13.909C11.2008 14.4877 10.7202 14.9683 10.1415 15.3025C9.65792 15.5817 9.12128 15.7009 8.49597 15.7576C7.87984 15.8134 7.11196 15.8133 6.14929 15.8133C5.18667 15.8133 4.41874 15.8134 3.80261 15.7576C3.1773 15.7009 2.64067 15.5817 2.1571 15.3025C1.5784 14.9683 1.09778 14.4877 0.76355 13.909C0.484366 13.4254 0.365184 12.8888 0.308472 12.2635C0.252649 11.6473 0.252808 10.8795 0.252808 9.9168C0.252808 8.95418 0.252664 8.18625 0.308472 7.57012C0.365184 6.94481 0.484366 6.40818 0.76355 5.92462C1.09777 5.34589 1.57839 4.86529 2.1571 4.53106C2.64067 4.25188 3.1773 4.13269 3.80261 4.07598C4.41